## 📁 Files Analyzed

| File | Lines | Role |
|---|---|---|
| [dashboard.blade.php](file:///c:/Users/Arween/OneDrive/Documents/DepEd_ZC%20-%20Inventory%20System/DepEd-ZC-Inventory-System-main/resources/views/dashboard.blade.php) | 316 | Main dashboard layout + sidebar + all sections |
| [inventory-setup.blade.php](file:///c:/Users/Arween/OneDrive/Documents/DepEd_ZC%20-%20Inventory%20System/DepEd-ZC-Inventory-System-main/resources/views/inventory-setup.blade.php) | 237 | Setup wizard (3-step JS-driven flow) |
| [login.blade.php](file:///c:/Users/Arween/OneDrive/Documents/DepEd_ZC%20-%20Inventory%20System/DepEd-ZC-Inventory-System-main/resources/views/auth/login.blade.php) | 77 | Email-only login |
| [register.blade.php](file:///c:/Users/Arween/OneDrive/Documents/DepEd_ZC%20-%20Inventory%20System/DepEd-ZC-Inventory-System-main/resources/views/auth/register.blade.php) | 243 | Registration with OTP flow (Alpine.js) |
| [auth.css](file:///c:/Users/Arween/OneDrive/Documents/DepEd_ZC%20-%20Inventory%20System/DepEd-ZC-Inventory-System-main/public/css/auth.css) | 39 | Auth-page styles, button effects, focus rings |
| [web.php](file:///c:/Users/Arween/OneDrive/Documents/DepEd_ZC%20-%20Inventory%20System/DepEd-ZC-Inventory-System-main/routes/web.php) | 43 | All route definitions |

---

## Key Design Patterns

- **Ultra-rounded cards** (`rounded-[2.5rem]`+) give a soft, premium feel
- **Uppercase micro-labels** (`text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest`) for form labels and section headers
- **Emoji as icons** (📊🏢✅⚠️📍⚙️🏫📦🔍) — no icon library dependency
- **Color-coded districts** — blue for LD1, emerald for LD2
- **Responsive sidebar** — fixed on desktop, slide-in overlay on mobile with backdrop blur
- **No password login** — email-only auth, matching the approval-based registration flow
